Scenes at Centocow Road in Centocow, near Underberg, KwaZulu-Natal. JOHANNESBURG - Seventy-two children have been injured in a school bus crash in Underberg, KwaZulu Natal. The bus they were travelling in overturned on a dirt road off the R617 near Centocow. READ: 21 schoolchildren injured in Carletonville collision Two children are in a critical condition in hospital. The cause of the crash is unknown at this time and authorities are investigating.